metadata.name: Flappy bird
metadata.description: Flappy Birds NFT Collection is a series of digital collectibles featuring the iconic characters and themes from the popular mobile game, Flappy Birds. Each NFT is unique and verified on a blockchain, providing ownership and scarcity for collectors. The collection includes rare and limited edition items, such as special characters and in-game items, making it a must-have for fans of the game and NFT enthusiasts. Get your hands on a piece of gaming history and add to your digital collection with Flappy Birds NFTs.
